  "Description": {
    "English": "A specialist device, created by Iteration Tethys. Its primary function is to hail your <span class=\"name name-technology\">reconstructed Sentinel drone</span>.<br><br>Select the device and use Deactivate Broadcast (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>) to stop signalling [ The Sentry ].<br><br>While this flare is active in your <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit inventory</span>, the drone will stay by your side while planetside.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "迭代：特提斯创造的特殊设备。主要用于呼叫你的<span class=\"name name-technology\">重构护卫无人机</span>。<br><br>选择设备并使用关闭广播（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）以停止向[哨兵]发送信号。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装库存</span>中激活信号器后，无人机将会在行星表面陪伴你。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "由迭代：忒堤斯製作的專家裝置。主要功能是呼喚<span class=\"name name-technology\">重建的巡警無人機</span>。<br><br>選擇裝置並關閉廣播 (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)，停止對 [哨兵] 發出訊號。<br><br>在你的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝道具欄</span>中開啟這個照明彈後，無人機就會在星球空間內伴隨著你。"
  },
